data.description: Highest and best Sunday 2-21-2021 by 7pm. Stunning Duplex in South Minneapolis. Great for owner occupant. Natural wood work.  Hardwood floors throughout.  Separate utilities, fenced in backyard. Lower unit is oversized one bedroom, upper unit has 4 bedrooms, tenants pay $1,700 per month. Two car Garage, Place is in excellent condition. Perfect for owner occupant. Great neighborhood,  Owner is a licensed real estate agent. Owner will pay outstanding assessments before closing Quick closing possible.  View unit 1 at first showing.
